==================================================
XRP Large-Scale Wallet Scanner (REAL-TIME FILE EXPLORER)
==================================================

Performance Optimizations Applied:
✅ Persistent requests.Session() with connection pooling
✅ HTTPAdapter with 100 connections / 100 pool size
✅ urllib3 Retry strategy
✅ TCP connection reuse & keep-alive
✅ Concurrent workers: 20 (was 5)
✅ Request delay: 0.02s (was 0.1s)
✅ Thread-local sessions for parallel processing
✅ Optimized batch processing

BLOCKCHAIN VALIDATION ENHANCEMENTS:
✅ DestinationTag must be absent or null
✅ Memos array must be absent or empty
✅ Transaction result must equal tesSUCCESS
✅ Only successful Payment transactions
✅ Valid delivered amount verification
✅ No false positives from tagged transactions

REAL-TIME FILE EXPLORER FEATURES (NEW):
✅ Live file links generated during scan
✅ Automatic file discovery via patterns
✅ CSV batches stream in real-time
✅ Preview partial results before scan completes
✅ Download files while scanning continues
✅ Auto-refreshing status endpoint
✅ Live explorer HTML page (/api/explorer/live/<scan_id>)
✅ Frontend-friendly data structure
✅ Supports millions of transactions

FILE MANAGEMENT FEATURES:
✅ Secure file download endpoint (/api/files/<filename>)
✅ Browser-viewable file preview (/api/files/view/<filename>)
✅ File explorer dashboard (/api/files/explorer/<scan_id>)
✅ Batch CSV management (/api/files/batch/<scan_id>)
✅ Automatic file links in scan status
✅ JSON pretty-printing for browser viewing
✅ CSV-to-HTML table conversion for previews
✅ Large file truncation for performance
✅ Path traversal protection
✅ File cleanup endpoint

THREAD SAFETY FIXES:
✅ Global active_scans dictionary defined
✅ Thread lock for concurrent access
✅ Proper error handling with graceful fallbacks
✅ Safe dictionary updates across multiple threads

Features:
✅ Standard scans (up to 1000 transactions)
✅ Large scans (millions of transactions)
✅ Automatic checkpointing
✅ Parallel batch processing
✅ Resume interrupted scans
✅ Real-time progress tracking
✅ Blockchain-verified missing tag detection
✅ File management and preview
✅ Live file streaming during scan

Endpoints:
  POST  /api/scan                    - Standard scan (verified)
  POST  /api/scan/large              - Start large scan (verified & fixed)
  GET   /api/scan/status/<id>        - Scan status with live file links
  GET   /api/scan/checkpoints        - List checkpoints
  POST  /api/scan/pause/<id>         - Pause scan
  POST  /api/scan/resume/<id>        - Resume scan
  GET   /api/analytics/summary       - Analytics
  GET   /api/files/<filename>        - Download file
  GET   /api/files/view/<filename>   - View file in browser
  GET   /api/files/explorer/<scan_id> - File explorer
  GET   /api/files/batch/<scan_id>   - Get batch files
  GET   /api/explorer/live/<scan_id> - Live explorer page
  POST  /api/files/cleanup           - Cleanup old files

